TYPES OF IP ADDRESS IN AWS
==========================
3 Types:

public IP: For outside access (it is dynamic ip). When we restart vm then public ip gets changed.
private IP : Fixed IP address for internal communication 
Elastic IP: Fixed public it (It is commercial )



